# STREAMING::IS_NEW_LOAD_SCENE_ACTIVE

## Summary
Returns true if a new load scene is active, false otherwise

## Returns
* **BOOL**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
check if a new load scene is currently running
